      "description": "Initial release.\n\n- Rename a file, a folder (recursively), or a multi-selection to slug-case from the file explorer context menu, or the whole vault from the command palette.\n- Preview modal listing every old → new path before anything changes.\n- Uses Obsidian's fileManager.renameFile, so links pointing to renamed files update automatically.\n- English and Spanish UI, following Obsidian's language setting.",
